********************************************
**************  gTaskmanager  **************
********************************************

gTaskmanager is a small taskmanager based on GTK+. You'll need at least
gtk v.2.8 to use this program.

You can check for new releases on http://oliwer.net. Please send bug reports
at Olivier Duclos <oliwer@free.fr>.


** Building **

./configure
make
make install (as root)

** Usage **

The GUI can be started by running 'gtaskmanager'.
